msgid "Entity Setup + Payroll Compliance (UF, SII, AFP, FONASA/ISAPRE)"
msgstr ""

#: home/templates/articles/cl/article_0001.html:1106
msgid ""
"Chile is one of Latin America's most stable and transparent economies — but "
"compliant hiring and payroll require navigating strict labour laws, complex "
"taxes, and local indices like UF."
msgstr ""

#: home/templates/articles/cl/article_0001.html:1113
